      <title>欧洲天然气期权购买量在近期价格波动期间猛增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/european-gas-options-buying-jumped-during-recent-price-swings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格的剧烈波动促使交易商纷纷买入期权合约，随着中东冲突风险升级，投资者寻求保护自己免受损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/european-gas-options-buying-jumped-during-recent-price-swings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 07:35:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
